data.description: NEW UPDATES JUST COMPLETED & READY FOR NEW OWNERS! LOCATED IN THE LOVELY SMALL BUT PLEASANT WHISPERING OAKS COMMUNITY NESTLED AMONG TALL OAKS & AWAY FROM CROWDED CITIES! SITTING JUST NORTH OF SR50/CORTEZ OFF 301 MINUTES FROM I-75. THIS HOME HAS MANY FEATURES THAT WOULD APPEAL TO MOST ANY BUYER IN ADDITION TO SPACIOUS OPEN FLOOR PLAN WITH HIGH CEILINGS THROUGHOUT PROVIDING AMBLE AMBIENT LIGHTING, WET BAR, FIREPLACE, SEPARATE OFFICE, BONUS FLORIDA ROOM & HUGE ENCLOSED/SCREENED LANAI. UPDATES INCLUDE ROOF 2020, ENCLOSED PORCH ROOF 2023, A/C 2022, WATER HEATER 2022 &  FRESH INTERIOR PAINT! ANNUAL TERMITE POLICY & HOME WARRANTY IN PLACE. THIS COMMUNITY OFFERS AN ACTIVE BUT PEACEFUL LIFESTYLE WITH NEARBY BIKING TRAILS, HOSPITALS, SHOPPING, CHURCHES & ENTERTAINMENT. LESS THAN AN HOUR AWAY ARE FLORIDA'S MAJOR ATTRACTIONS, SPRINGS AND BEACHES. BRING YOUR GOLF CART AS MANY COMMUNITY EVENTS THROUGHOUT THE YEAR.
